76
00:04:55,156 --> 00:04:59,680
And if not for me, you and he wouldn't have such a rift.

77
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:02,180
It's all my fault.

78
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:04,212
If it weren't for my entry into this family,

79
00:05:04,212 --> 00:05:08,400
