102
00:07:07,380 --> 00:07:09,560
What were you thinking?

103
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,740
President Gu, I'm sorry.

104
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:23,620
This morning, I didn't mean to offend you.

105
00:07:23,620 --> 00:07:24,960
I was just…

106
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:28,560
I-I just heard our company's investment deal would fall through.

107
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:33,040
I cared about our company too much, and I was too anxious so I couldn't help it.

108
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:35,888
I really didn't mean to offend you.

109
00:07:35,888 --> 00:07:39,212
President Gu, I'm sorry.

110
00:07:44,512 --> 00:07:47,280
