111
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,848
Sor...

112
00:07:50,816 --> 00:07:52,536
Assistant Sheng?

113
00:07:52,536 --> 00:07:55,780
Zhao Nuan Nuan, your apology lacks sincerity.

114
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:59,280
You said to help the company, you did something to the president.

115
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:02,300
I didn't hear clearly. Say it again.

116
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:04,340
Zhao Nuan Nuan, wait a moment!

117
00:08:11,104 --> 00:08:14,320
Let me tell you this. The president is still lying in bed

118
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:16,400
this morning due to your kiss.

119
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:19,232
It's almost like a work-related injury.

120
00:08:19,232 --> 00:08:24,060
As the one who did this, shouldn't you personally visit him?

121
00:08:24,060 --> 00:08:27,360
- I-Is he not well?
- Of course, he's not.

122
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:31,240
Such a serious thing happened. How can he possibly be okay?

123
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,060
I'll tell you this.

124
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:38,664
That was Gu Yi Chen's first kiss,

125
00:08:38,664 --> 00:08:40,500
