126
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:43,760
Tell me, how will you compensate?

127
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:57,360
Here's the pass code to his home.

128
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,000
Just go.

129
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:10,160
<i>Yi Chen, you must always remember </i>

130
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:12,372
<i> who brought us to this point</i>

131
00:09:12,372 --> 00:09:14,780
<i>and who betrayed us.</i>

132
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:22,220
