141
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:36,960
Assistant Sheng told me to come.

142
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,708
He gave me your home's pass code.

143
00:10:38,708 --> 00:10:41,140
Don't move! Don't come near me!

144
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:43,720
President Gu, don't get upset. I just wanted to explain…

145
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,440
About that kiss…

146
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,980
All right, don't say anymore. Don't move!

147
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:49,540
Stay one meter away… No, two meters! Just stand there!

148
00:10:49,540 --> 00:10:51,080
That's right.

149
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,856
President Gu?

150
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:59,960
One minute you want me to stay, and the next you don't want me near.

151
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,860
You want me to pretend to be your girlfriend,

152
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:03,900
