153
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:07,340
Do you think you're a chameleon? You are so good at changing.

154
00:11:43,936 --> 00:11:45,724
President Gu?

155
00:11:53,696 --> 00:11:56,260
- Why are you chuckling?
- I'm smiling at you.

156
00:11:56,260 --> 00:11:58,756
You are 10,000 times cuter than at the office.

157
00:11:58,756 --> 00:12:00,560
- "Cute"?
- Yes.

158
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,776
This is my first time seeing you in pajamas,

159
00:12:02,776 --> 00:12:06,440
and my first time seeing your hair like that.

160
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:08,992
Isn't it cute?

161
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:12,340
Assistant Sheng said you weren't feeling well

162
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:14,400
