163
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:17,680
I'll cook you porridge. Maybe it will help you feel better.

164
00:12:19,104 --> 00:12:21,060
Can you cook porridge?

165
00:12:21,060 --> 00:12:25,740
Of course. I'm the top chef under my mother.

166
00:12:31,872 --> 00:12:34,024
What's this?

167
00:12:36,128 --> 00:12:37,752
President Gu...

168
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:40,944
The milk is mine.

169
00:12:40,944 --> 00:12:43,860
Clearly, I was the one who gave it to you.

170
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:45,460
It's mine.

171
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:47,060
You…

172
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:56,060
Gu Yi Chen, since this morning at the office,

173
00:12:56,060 --> 00:13:01,240
I have been wondering what happened to you.

174
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:04,860
Why have you seemed a little odd

175
00:13:04,860 --> 00:13:07,520
