176
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:11,784
And why did you faint?

177
00:13:12,576 --> 00:13:17,864
Could it really be because of that

178
00:13:17,864 --> 00:13:19,576
kiss?

179
00:13:19,576 --> 00:13:25,880
Was it really because that was your first kiss?

180
00:13:41,056 --> 00:13:42,120
No way?

181
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,200
No.

182
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,480
Why not ask someone else?

183
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,520
<i>It's delicious.</i>

184
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:47,280
<i>Just make a few more phone calls and ask around.</i>

185
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:49,180
<i>Don't worry about the hassle.</i>

186
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:51,200
I'm off work now, Sister Xin Ran. See you tomorrow.

187
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:54,280
- Bye bye.
- Mi Mi, this isn't done yet.

188
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:56,700
<i>[Z.M.G. Tech.com]</i>

189
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:57,980
- Go home and wait for my call.
- Okay.

190
00:13:57,980 --> 00:14:00,640
<i>- I'll send it to you when I'm done.
- Okay.</i>

191
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:11,288
- Are you off?
- I'm working overtime.

192
00:14:11,288 --> 00:14:13,344
- Have you...
- I don't have time.

193
00:14:23,540 --> 00:14:26,260
Allergic to being touched by females?

194
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:34,524
What kind of strange disease is this?

195
00:14:34,524 --> 00:14:37,220
So you also think it's a strange disease.

196
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:39,220
N-No.

197
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:43,340
In my father's eyes and everyone else, who hears about this disease,

198
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:48,244
they feel I'm a freak with a strange disease.

199
00:14:49,404 --> 00:14:52,636
I got this disease after my mother passed away.

200
00:14:52,636 --> 00:14:56,228
The worst was when I couldn't breathe

201
00:14:56,228 --> 00:14:59,840
due to the allergy, and even my heart almost stopped.

202
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:06,940
<i>Yi Chen, surprise!</i>

203
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:12,040
<i>Luo Yi?</i>

204
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:15,640
<i>Aren't you happy? I flew back from California just to see you.</i>

205
00:15:19,456 --> 00:15:21,920
<i>Yi Chen, what's wrong? Yi Chen?</i>

206
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:25,000
<i>- Yi Chen, what's wrong?
- Stay away from me. Don't come near me!</i>

207
00:15:25,620 --> 00:15:27,740
<i>- Are you all right?
- Stay away from me.</i>

208
00:15:30,016 --> 00:15:31,672
<i>Don't come near.</i>

209
00:15:34,528 --> 00:15:36,100
<i>Yi Chen?</i>

210
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:38,204
<i>Yi Chen?</i>

211
00:15:39,660 --> 00:15:41,632
<i>Yi Chen, are you all right?</i>

212
00:15:41,632 --> 00:15:44,140
<i>Yi Chen, wake up! Yi Chen!</i>

213
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,260
No way.

214
00:15:49,260 --> 00:15:54,360
That's why my office has an unspoken rule of not allowing unknown women to come in.

215
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:57,460
It's not because I have any prejudice against women,

216
00:15:57,460 --> 00:16:00,940
but because of my allergies.

217
00:16:00,940 --> 00:16:05,320
Due to this strange disease, I was at odds with my father for more than a decade.

218
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:09,640
I also can't get close to those aunties who care about me.

219
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:14,400
When at a family gathering, I can only watch them from a distance.

220
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:15,700
I can't get closer.

221
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:19,320
Because once I get close to them, my allergy reacts.

222
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:21,720
Over the years,

223
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:23,540
I have been alone;

224
00:16:23,540 --> 00:16:27,560
I eat alone, work alone,

225
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:29,760
and live alone.

226
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:34,380
For everything, I have only myself.

227
00:16:34,380 --> 00:16:37,556
But why did I...

228
00:16:40,416 --> 00:16:42,220
<i>Oh my.</i>

229
00:16:42,220 --> 00:16:44,860
<i>I even wanted to share his good luck,</i>

230
00:16:44,860 --> 00:16:47,280
<i>and I...</i>

231
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:51,200
You're the exception. I'm not allergic to you.

232
00:16:52,308 --> 00:16:54,264
Why?

233
00:16:54,264 --> 00:16:58,760
The last time we met in the hotel, you put a sticky note on my face.

234
00:16:58,760 --> 00:17:02,380
But it didn't trigger my allergy.

235
00:17:02,380 --> 00:17:04,500
That time at the hotel?

236
00:17:05,380 --> 00:17:09,624
My psychologist said you may have some kind of feature

237
00:17:09,624 --> 00:17:14,300
or lack a feature so you don't trigger my allergies.

238
00:17:15,140 --> 00:17:16,920
Lacking?

239
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,720
So am I lacking something?

240
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:27,496
Is it that you're not feminine enough?

241
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:35,944
Thank you for the compliment, President Gu.

242
00:17:36,704 --> 00:17:38,320
What are you doing?

243
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:42,240
Bringing you the porridge, CEO Gu.

244
00:17:50,460 --> 00:17:54,520
Boss, why don't you just rent it to us?

245
00:17:55,328 --> 00:17:56,900
That's really not possible.

246
00:18:12,840 --> 00:18:14,720
